{"questionId":"12265","questionHtml":"<p class=\"indent1\" style=\"margin-top:12pt;text-align:left;\">Given the matrix <strong><em>A</em></strong> =&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  3&amp;2 \\\\   { - 1}&amp;0  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> find the values of the real number <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"k\">\n  <mi>k</mi>\n</math></span> for which <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{det}}\\left( {A - kI} \\right) = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>det</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>A</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mi>I</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span> where&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"I = \\left( {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  1&amp;0 \\\\   0&amp;1  \\end{array}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>I</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>0</mn>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span></p>\n<p class=\"indent1\" style=\"margin-top:12pt;text-align:left;\">&nbsp;</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{det}}\\left( {A - kI} \\right) = 0\">\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>det</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>A</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mi>I</mi>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow \\left| {\\begin{array}{*{20}{c}}  {3 - k}&amp;2 \\\\   { - 1}&amp;{ - k}  \\end{array}} \\right| = 0\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>|</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mtable rowspacing=\"4pt\" columnspacing=\"1em\">\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>k</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n        <mtr>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n          <mtd>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>−</mo>\n              <mi>k</mi>\n            </mrow>\n          </mtd>\n        </mtr>\n      </mtable>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>|</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow {k^2} - 3k + 2 = 0\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>3</mn>\n  <mi>k</mi>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow \\left( {k - 2} \\right)\\left( {k - 1} \\right) = 0\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>2</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mi>k</mi>\n      <mo>−</mo>\n      <mn>1</mn>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\" \\Rightarrow k = 1{\\text{,}}\\,\\,2\">\n  <mo stretchy=\"false\">⇒</mo>\n  <mi>k</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>1</mn>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mn>2</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(A2)</strong></em>&nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>(C4)</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[4 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"12265","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.42","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Given the matrix A = ( 3 2 − 1 0 ) find the values of the real number k for which det ( A − k I ) = 0 where I = ( 1 0 0 1 )","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"42","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 4]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","AHL 1.15—Eigenvalues and eigenvectors"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}